The Activation ("Brahma dejo abhivruthyartam..."): “For the growth of divine splendor/knowledge (Brahma Tejas)...”

This is the "re-installation." You are not just putting on a thread; you are plugging yourself back into the source of Brahma Tejas (the energy of creation and wisdom). You are setting a high-performance intention for the coming year.

